---
title: Golden Kumara & Israeli Couscous Salad with Almonds & Plant-Based Basil Pesto Mayo
description: Quick and easy, that’s the best kind of dinner. Roast the kumara in our Aussie spice blend and then whip up a fluffy couscous and have
it ready to be gobbled down in no time at all. Top it off with a plant-based basil pesto mayo to ensure there won’t be any crumbs left.

